<span class="label">Research</span>
<h2>Anthropomorphism and Human-Robot Interaction</h2>
<h6 class="subheader"></h6>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By Rae Yule Kim
<br/>
Communications of the ACM,
February 2024,
Vol. 67 No. 2, Pages 80-85<br/>
10.1145/3624716<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
</span>
